Development notes
=================

This repository may contain local build outputs such as .config, vmlinux,
System.map, object files, and generated command files. They are not required
source files for the port.

When changing NUC980 platform support:

    1. Update the relevant driver, DTS, or defconfig.
    2. Rebuild zImage and dtbs.
    3. Boot-test on the target NUC980 board.
    4. Check early console output on ttyS0 at 115200 8N1 unless your board
       uses a different UART.

For upstream Linux development rules and coding style, continue to follow the
documentation under Documentation/process/.
